Types of Projects in SAP

1. Implementation

Implementation - In these types of projects, Customer is implementing SAP for the first time. 
All Legacy system data needs to be migrated to the SAP system.


2. Support

Support - It is also called as Maintenance project.
Customer is running his business through SAP. Customer requires support for the daily issues,
tickets, and new change requests (CR).


3. UPgrade

Upgrade: In this type of project, customer is moving from older version of SAP to
higher version of SAP.


4. Roll out

Roll out: In this type of project, the existing SAP system is going to implement
for different countries/region.
